In the spiral the numbers are arranged on integer lattice points  
\((x,y)\) where the origin \((0,0)\) contains 1, \(x\!+\!1\) rightward, \(y\!+\!1\) upward.  

For a point \((x,y)\) let  

\[
t=\max(|x|,|y|),\qquad s=2t+1 ,\qquad M=s^{2}
\]

\(M\) is the largest number in the “ring’’ \(t\).  
The position of \((x,y)\) on that ring is given by an “offset’’ \(k\) measured counter‑clockwise
starting from the bottom‑right corner \((t,-t)\).  

The offset \(k\) is

```
if y == -t:            k = t - x
else if x == -t:       k = 2t + (y + t)
else if y ==  t:       k = 4t + (x + t)
else                   k = 6t + (t - y)       # x == t
```

The number at \((x,y)\) is

\[
N = M - k .
\]

--------------------------------------------------------------------

### The number 2026

We find its coordinates:

*\(t=23\) because \(2026=(47^{2}+1)\).  
*The first number of layer \(t=23\) is \((t,-(t-1))=(23,-22)\).  
So \(2026\) sits at \((23,-22)\).

--------------------------------------------------------------------

### The eight neighbours

For each of the eight relative positions we compute the Cartesian
coordinates, their offsets and finally their numbers.

| neighbour | \((x,y)\) | \(t\) | \(k\) | \(M\) | \(N\) |
|-----------|-----------|-------|-------|-------|--------|
| (22,-23)  | (22,-23) | 23 | \(23-22=1\) | 2209 | 2208 |
| (22,-22)  | (22,-22) | 22 | \(22-22=0\) | 2025 | 2025 |
| (22,-21)  | (22,-21) | 22 | \(6\!\cdot\!22+(22-(-21)) =175\) | 2025 | 1850 |
| (23,-23)  | (23,-23) | 23 | \(23-23=0\) | 2209 | 2209 |
| (23,-21)  | (23,-21) | 23 | \(6\!\cdot\!23+(23-(-21)) =182\) | 2209 | 2027 |
| (24,-23) | (24,-23) | 24 | \(6\!\cdot\!24+(24-(-23)) =191\) | 2401 | 2210 |
| (24,-22) | (24,-22) | 24 | \(6\!\cdot\!24+(24-(-22)) =190\) | 2401 | 2211 |
| (24,-21) | (24,-21) | 24 | \(6\!\cdot\!24+(24-(-21)) =189\) | 2401 | 2212 |

--------------------------------------------------------------------

### Sum

\[
\begin{aligned}
\text{Sum} &= 2208+2025+1850+2209+2027+2210+2211+2212 \\
           &= 16952 .
\end{aligned}
\]

--------------------------------------------------------------------
\[
\boxed{16952}
\]
